Titolo: Soulcalibur: Lost Swords

Anno: 2014

Descrizione: Soulcalibur: Lost Swords was a free-to-play fighting game distributed through PlayStation Network. Released in 2014, the game is based on Soulcalibur V and is strictly single-player. It uses the same weapon-based fighting system from previous games; however, several of the gameplay mechanics were changed, simplified or otherwise removed. 
The game was also periodically updated with new content, including new events, items, and characters. The game ceased operations effective in 2015.

Genere: Fighting 

Valutazione: N/A
